summary: Provides a template for a local Feast feature repository, including a sample configuration of entities, data sources, feature views, request and push sources, on‑demand transformations, feature services, and logging, together with helper utilities to fetch historical and online feature values and run a simple demonstration of the store.
business_intent: Enable developers to quickly set up, explore, and validate a Feast feature store locally, supporting end‑to‑end feature engineering workflows and automated testing before moving to production.
